Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">. 1-2.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ἈπολλονίουἈπολλωνίου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ἈπολλονίουἈπολλωνίου\">....]ΛΟΝΙΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΕΖΩ[.].Ι\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΕΝΙΑΥΤΟ.Σ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>Ζ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ....ΛΟΝΙΟΥἈπολλονίου\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003975_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003975_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003975.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003975-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Meligunìs Lipára XII\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: ΕΖΩΚΕΙ \u003Cspan>Libertini\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">  \u003Ch3>Commentary translated from ILipara\u003C/h3>  \u003Cp>There are no traces of lines above the first visible line. Libertini, who identified the stone as a stele rather than a cladding slab observed: \"The first part of the name is missing, though the stele appears intact\". On the other hand, the letters missing at the beginning of line 1, one or two, don't seem sufficient to reconstruct a full name. The proposed reading is based on the hypothesis that the first part of the name, maybe a patronymic preceeded by another name, was inscribed on another slab, contiguous with the preserved one.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Libertini 1921 225 no.46 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001875\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001875\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> \u2028 Bernabó-Brea\u2028 Cavalier\u2028 Campagna\u2028 2003 352 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Lines 1-4  55-65  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[203,206,209,212,215,218,221,224],{"id":204,"html":205},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Simona Stoyanova\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">. 1-2.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ἈπολλονίουἈπολλωνίου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ἈπολλονίουἈπολλωνίου\">Ἀπολ]λονίου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ἐζώ[κ]ε̣ι \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἐνιαυτοὺ̣ς \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ζ´ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ....ΛΟΝΙΟΥἈπολλονίου\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Simona Stoyanova\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">. 1-2.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ἈπολλονίουἈπολλωνίου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ἈπολλονίουἈπολλωνίου\">....]ΛΟΝΙΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΕΖΩ[.].Ι\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΕΝΙΑΥΤΟ.Σ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>Ζ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ....ΛΟΝΙΟΥἈπολλονίου\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":207,"html":208},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003975_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003975_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003975.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003975-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":210,"html":211},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Meligunìs Lipára XII\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: ΕΖΩΚΕΙ \u003Cspan>Libertini\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":213,"html":214},"translation","\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{